# News Categorization AI - Executive Summary

## üéØ Project Goal
Built an AI system that automatically categorizes news articles into 4 topics (World, Sports, Business, Technology) with 90%+ accuracy.

## üíº Business Impact
- **95% reduction** in manual classification time
- **60% cost savings** through model optimization
- **50+ articles/second** processing capability
- **Real-time predictions** with confidence scoring

## üîß Technical Highlights

### Models Developed
1. **BERT Model**: 92% accuracy, 45ms inference
2. **DistilBERT Model**: 90.5% accuracy, 18ms inference (production deployment)

### Key Achievements
- Fine-tuned transformer models on 120,000 articles
- Conducted comprehensive A/B testing (BERT vs DistilBERT)
- Implemented confidence-based quality control (95% precision threshold)
- Deployed interactive demo with batch processing capabilities

## üìä Results Summary

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Overall Accuracy | 92% (BERT), 90.5% (DistilBERT) |
| Speed Improvement | 2.5x faster with DistilBERT |
| Cost Reduction | 60% lower inference costs |
| Model Size | 40% smaller (DistilBERT) |
| Articles Processed | 7,600 test samples |

## üõ†Ô∏è Technology Stack
- **Languages**: Python
- **ML Frameworks**: PyTorch, Transformers (Hugging Face)
- **Models**: BERT, DistilBERT
- **Tools**: Pandas, scikit-learn, Gradio, Matplotlib
- **Platform**: Google Colab

## üìà Development Process

1. **Data Exploration** - EDA on 120K articles, baseline model (87%)
2. **Model Development** - BERT fine-tuning (92% accuracy)
3. **Optimization** - DistilBERT comparison (efficiency analysis)
4. **Evaluation** - Confusion matrices, error analysis, threshold tuning
5. **Deployment** - Interactive demo with batch processing

## üéì Skills Demonstrated
- Machine Learning & Deep Learning
- Natural Language Processing
- Transfer Learning & Fine-Tuning
- Model Optimization & A/B Testing
- Data Analysis & Visualization
- Software Engineering & Documentation
- Production Deployment

## üìù Key Learnings
- **Model Selection**: Quantified accuracy vs. efficiency trade-offs
- **Error Analysis**: Identified Business-Technology overlap as main challenge
- **Production Readiness**: Implemented human-in-the-loop for low-confidence cases
- **Scalability**: Optimized for real-world deployment constraints

